r />\n好似apple pay入信用卡一樣姐，都係用緊信用卡，只係方便咗，令人更易洗錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你估Apple 善堂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用得佢既野，就要比交易費用，八達通食開100%，會唔會分啲出黎比其他人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯，除非你話用左之後可以搵得多過而家，否則都冇咩可能。"},{"pid":"ecaf01574c81171b2893abba120d616bd16dd441","tid":19033,"uid":38390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T17:09:04.000Z","msg":"無，只想所有地方支援master visa"},{"pid":"da520f52142beb3cc3939954ce4c95ea7d415c5b","tid":19033,"uid":40744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T17:11:42.000Z","msg":"如果 tap&amp;go 繼續壯大<br />\n我覺得會"},{"pid":"d48815188c1191cb12c867453893d3fa497c864f","tid":19033,"uid":32661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T17:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔夠實體卡快<br />\n英國張oyster card用到contactless超過一年<br />\n都唔係見太多人用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSuica Apple Pay 係真係有獨立chip係入面<br />\n比sw simulation (oyster)係快好多<br />\n本身Apple 唔想加hardware <br />\n但因為Suica 要求要係200ms之內要完成transaction <br />\n用sw 唔得先加hardware <br />\n實際用應該比卡更快<br />\n因為唔洗磨袋"},{"pid":"e1937a7349fe78c4542cfd5d65c7fd947a58cd52","tid":19033,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:18:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔夠實體卡快<br />\n英國張oyster card用到contactless超過一年<br />\n都唔係見太多人用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為無得買travelcard同railcard,用香港做例子就係無得買全月通果d"},{"pid":"85ff669cc7c06f553ca1c06f20e2fe9f6ae3aebe","tid":19033,"uid":8511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔夠實體卡快<br />\n英國張oyster card用到contactless超過一年<br />\n都唔係見太多人用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為無得買travelcard同railcard,用香港做例子就係無得買全月通果d</blockquote><br />\niphone 都出到7啦, 要做點會無辦法"},{"pid":"91833fff653c361e1e686a0bed371e424b21e6fc","tid":19033,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:29:37.000Z","msg":"即係可以直接用部iPhone入閘？"},{"pid":"b745838eb5de0c3330c2540508c306288e8a31ee",